text: Jessica Marcela Parra Rojas (born 10 August 1995) is a Colombian professional racing cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Women's Continental Team . ==Major results== ;2014 : 3rd Team pursuit, Central American and Caribbean Games (with Valentina Paniagua, Milena Salcedo and Lorena Vargas) ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Colombian female cyclists Category:Sportspeople from Bogotá Category:Pan American Games medalists in cycling Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for Colombia Category:Cyclists at the 2019 Pan American Games
